headline: PSEG Increases 2026 Common Stock Dividend
summary: The Board of Directors of Public Service Enterprise Group (NYSE: PEG) declared a $0.67 per share quarterly common stock dividend for the first quarter of 2026, payable on or before March 31, 2026, to shareholders of record on March 10, 2026. This action represents an increase of $0.04 per share in the company's quarterly common stock dividend, bringing the 2026 indicative annual rate to $2.68 per share.
